        <mxCell id="WgSi36YBb3g61TZYZooB-783" value="&lt;b&gt;ty&lt;/b&gt; = &lt;b&gt;warpid / (BN/TN/WarpX) &lt;/b&gt;* WarpY&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; // block层面&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; + &lt;b&gt;groupid / (WarpX / 2)&lt;/b&gt; * WarpY&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;// warp层面&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; + &lt;b&gt;glaneid / 2&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;// thread层面" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;fontSize=12;" parent="1" vertex="1">
